  "title": "Sales Engineer (Water Quality/Scientific/Analytical Instruments)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Manage and support the distributor network in Southeast Asia, ensuring alignment with business objectives.</li>\n  <li>Identify opportunities to appoint and develop new distributors in untapped markets.</li>\n  <li>Collaborate with distributors to plan market-specific sales strategies and meet sales targets.</li>\n  <li>Track distributor performance, provide feedback, and support them with training, events, and customer visits.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Degree in Chemical Engineering or equivalent.</li>\n  <li>At least 2 years’ experience <strong>managing distributors</strong> in <strong>scientific or analytical instruments.</strong></li>\n  <li>Strong interpersonal and communication skills, with technical aptitude in related equipment.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you are keen to apply for the position, kindly email your detailed resume in<strong> MS Word </strong>to <strong>hr@recruit-expert.com</strong></p>\n<p>Please note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>\n<p>For more job opportunities, please visit our website at <a href=\"http://www.recruit-expert.com/\"><strong>www.recruit-expert.com</strong></a></p>\n<p>EA Licence: 19C9701</p>\n<p>Registration: R1326740</p>",
